data.description: You'll want to see this expansive 4-bedroom home with 3 full bathrooms. As you enter, you're greeted by a sizable mudroom that doubles as an office. The kitchen has been modernized with custom cabinets, quartz surfaces, and contemporary stainless steel appliances. Adjacent to the kitchen is a dining area, perfect for hosting, with patio doors opening to the rear deck. The inviting living area is adorned with stone details. The generously sized master suite boasts vaulted ceilings, a jetted bathtub, a separate shower, and a walk-in wardrobe. The upper level houses 3 bedrooms and a renovated bathroom. The property also features a heated garage for one car. Enjoy the 24x52 above-ground pool with an 8x16 deck to keep cool during the summers. Wind down by the firepit in the backyard after a tiring day. Numerous upgrades have been made, such as new siding, entrance doors, a 50-gallon water heater, furnace, water pump, pressure tank, and updates to the electrical and plumbing systems. The current owner has meticulously maintained this residence, and now it's ready for you. Book your visit now!
